snippet.title: Millennium 5 The Battle of the Millennium Trailer
snippet.description:
Available here:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/298850

Made with Adobe After Effects, Trapcode Form, and Trapcode Particular, this is the final video in a set of trailers made for the Millennium video game series.
